{"type": "article", "id": 13107, "title": "“经纬”桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-06T06:49:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122455z9xv370sdj6LHwOP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套名为 “经纬” 的家具和它的名字一样横平竖直，其中的“经线”部分可以随意移动，从而营造出不同的空间，根据用户的意愿收纳物品。这一系列里面有咖啡桌，高脚桌，边桌等不同类型的桌子，配色主打黄色，绿色和蓝色，与木质材料配合，看上去清新自然。这是<a href=\"http://www.juliegaillard.com/mobilier-latitude/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140735tga47ezbqM06iGLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140736MBO1A3sLNKHdhWkX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140736gC3O9JUzx5QpyF1d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140736OAgd6vNtF7acyXYj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.495\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140737C1uYilc9NqWBHUpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140737HsfACq8PhNkSM1vZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140737TuG4gUJZCRp1lD5O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140738zTJ1vwySNXIE2j6Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140738fHVcUTorwjOZD5sN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140738CnJXPQhs613iHpOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}